    "S": "Quick and Easy Pho"
  },
  "description": {
    "S": "This easy Vietnamese inspired Pho is a quick adaptation that's perfect when you're tight on time. Made with rice noodles, savory broth, and your choice of chicken, beef, pork or shrimp, topped with fresh herbs and garnishes."
